《'''瘸腿野马'''》（或译《'''跛行之马'''》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://store.windmusic.com.tw/zh/CD/TCD-1728|publisher=[[风潮音乐|风潮音乐]]|title=哈薩克冬不拉音樂|accessdate=2020-11-08|archive-date=2017-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170707194707/http://store.windmusic.com.tw/zh/CD/TCD-1728|dead-url=no}}</ref>，{{lang-kk|Ақсақ құлан|translit=Aqsaq qulan|translation=瘸腿的[[亚洲野驴|亚洲野驴]]}}）是[[哈萨克人|哈萨克人]]的一首传统[[冬不拉|冬不拉]]{{link-kk|奎依|Күй}}乐曲。

奎依乐曲通常伴随着相关的[[传说|传说]]故事。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://ich.unesco.org/en/RL/kazakh-traditional-art-of-dombra-kuy-00996|title=Kazakh traditional art of Dombra Kuy|website=[[联合国教科文组织|联合国教科文组织]]|language=en|accessdate=2020-11-08|archive-date=2020-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201207233119/https://ich.unesco.org/en/RL/kazakh-traditional-art-of-dombra-kuy-00996|dead-url=no}}</ref>《瘸腿野马》的故事与[[成吉思汗|成吉思汗]]及其长子[[朮赤|朮赤汗]]有关，在哈萨克人中无人不知。<ref>{{cite web|script-title=kk:ҚАЗАҚ ХАНДЫҒЫНА 550 ЖЫЛ: Жошы өлімін Шыңғыс ханға Кетбұғаның естіртуі|url=https://www.inform.kz/kz/kazak-handygyna-550-zhyl-zhoshy-olimin-shyngys-hanga-ketbuganyn-estirtui-dala-zandylygy-s-kaskabasov_a2748829|website=inform.kz|language=kk|agency=[[哈通社|哈通社]]|date=2015-02-22|accessdate=2020-11-08|archive-date=2021-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117131624/https://www.inform.kz/kz/kazak-handygyna-550-zhyl-zhoshy-olimin-shyngys-hanga-ketbuganyn-estirtui-dala-zandylygy-s-kaskabasov_a2748829|dead-url=no}}</ref>传说朮赤汗在打猎时射伤了一匹野马（一种似马似驴的动物，中文称[[亚洲野驴|亚洲野驴]]），在追赶过程中却被野马踢中身亡。成吉思汗命人寻找朮赤的踪迹，并且要往带来坏消息的人喉咙里灌[[铅|铅水]]。哈萨克{{link-kk|吉饶|Жырау|乐手}}{{link-kk|凯特布哈|Кетбұға}}自告奋勇去见成吉思汗。他问大汗：谁能让浑浊的江河源头变清？谁能让根部枯萎的树木重生？大汗表示那只有朮赤可以做到。然后凯特布哈演奏了《瘸腿野马》，用音乐展现朮赤之死的场面。成吉思汗听后又悲伤又愤怒。因为诉说坏消息的不是凯特布哈，而是他弹奏的[[冬不拉|冬不拉]]（一说{{le|阔布孜|Kobyz}}），因此只好往琴身上灌铅水，从此冬不拉就有了[[音孔|音孔]]。<ref name=Kuy>{{cite journal|last=Mukhambetova|first=Asiya|title=Philosophical Problems of Being in the Art of the Kazakh Küyshi|journal=Yearbook for Traditional Music|year=1990|page=36-41|volume=22|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.inform.kz/ru/v-ust-kamenogorske-prezentovali-knigu-k-830-letiyu-velikogo-skazitelya-ketbuga_a2719784|script-title=ru:В Усть-Каменогорске презентовали книгу к 830-летию великого сказителя Кетбуга|website=inform.kz|language=ru|agency=[[哈通社|哈通社]]|date=2014-11-24|accessdate=2020-11-08|archive-date=2018-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180226193554/http://www.inform.kz/ru/v-ust-kamenogorske-prezentovali-knigu-k-830-letiyu-velikogo-skazitelya-ketbuga_a2719784|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|title=中国民间故事集成 新疆卷 上|location=北京|publisher=中国ISBN中心|year=2008|isbn=7-5076-0297-4}}</ref>{{rp|540-541}}

这则故事成为了许多改编作品的基础。1968年，{{link-kk|哈萨克影业|Қазақфильм}}制作了12分钟的[[动画电影|动画短片]]《瘸腿野马》（{{lang|kk|Ақсақ құлан}}）。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://kazakhfilmstudios.kz/kaz/movies/6600/|script-title=kk:Аксак кулан / Ақсақ құлан|language=ru|publisher={{link-kk|哈萨克影业|Қазақфильм}}|accessdate=2020-11-08|archive-date=2021-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117131548/https://kazakhfilmstudios.kz/kaz/movies/6600/|dead-url=no}}</ref>1982年，[[中国哈萨克族|中国哈萨克族]]作家[[艾克拜尔·米吉提|艾克拜尔·米吉提]]在《[[人民文学|人民文学]]》上发表了[[短篇小说|短篇小说]]《瘸腿野马》。<ref>{{cite book|title=《人民文学》1983年短篇小说选|location=长沙|publisher=湖南人民出版社|year=1984|unified=10109·1713}}</ref>

[[吉尔吉斯人|吉尔吉斯人]]中也有同样的故事，只是冬不拉变成了吉尔吉斯的代表性乐器[[火不思|火不思]]。<ref name=silkroad/>{{rp|72}}<ref name=Kuy/>

据考证，故事的源头来自[[波斯|波斯]][[萨珊王朝|萨珊王朝]]。传说“得胜王”[[霍斯劳二世|霍斯劳二世]]心爱的骏马{{link-en|沙布德兹|Shabdiz}}生病之后，国王声称，谁要是带来了马死去的消息，就把谁杀掉。沙布德兹死后，宫廷乐师{{link-en|巴尔巴德|Barbad}}前去给霍斯劳演奏乐曲。国王听得十分动情，说：“沙布德兹死了！”因为是霍斯劳自己说出的消息，因此无人受到惩罚。巴尔巴德使用的乐器是{{link-en|巴尔巴特|Barbat_(lute)}}，与冬不拉和火不思同属有颈[[拨弦乐器|拨弦乐器]]，有着密切的关系。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Browne|first=Edward G.|title=The Sources of Dawlatshāh; with some Remarks on the Materials available for a Literary History of Persia, and an Excursus on Bārbad and Rūdagī|journal=Journal of the Royal Asiatic Society|volume=31|issue=1|year=1899|page=37-69|language=en|url=https://zenodo.org/record/1742176/files/article.pdf|access-date=2020-11-08|archive-date=2019-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190503064516/https://zenodo.org/record/1742176/files/article.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://iranicaonline.org/articles/barbad-minstrel|title=Bārbad|publisher=[[伊朗百科全书|伊朗百科全书]]|language=en|accessdate=2020-11-08|archive-date=2020-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926091258/https://iranicaonline.org/articles/barbad-minstrel|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=silkroad>{{cite book|last=Millward|first=James A.|title=''The Silk Road: a very short introduction''|isbn=9780199790791|publisher=[[Oxford_University_Press|Oxford University Press]]|year=2013|language=en}}</ref>{{rp|71-72}}

